   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Has measured [- - -, son/daughter] of Antonius, [- - -] eighteen [- - -] artabai [of wheat], total 18 [- -] artabai of wheat. I, Aurelius Ptolemaios, [son of - - -(?)], councillor, have signed. And likewise, (- - -?) the same has measured [- - - artabai] of wheat, which are for the harvest [of year . . . while I retain] my claim to the [other debts you owe me]. Year 13 of Lucius Septimius Severus Pius and Marcus Aurelius Antoninus Augusti, month day].</ab>
         </div>
